fu.util

Class MultiValueHashtable<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fu.util.MultiValueHashtable<K,V>

  • public class MultiValueHashtable<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    A hashtable that stores multiple value under a single key, i.e. subsequent put() with the same key, stores a list of values.
